---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout>
<!-- HERO SECTION -->
    <section class="hero about-hero" aria-labelledby="page-title">
      <div class="hero-content">
        <div class="hero-text">
          <span class="hero-badge">About Our Clinic</span>
          <h1 id="page-title">
            A Clinical Approach Built Around<br/>
            <span class="highlight">Clarity, Pace & Respect</span>
          </h1>
          <p class="hero-subtitle">
            Dr Anita Sharma works with adults, adolescents, children, and families who want a calmer, clearer first step into mental health or developmental care. The focus is not only on naming a concern, but on understanding what is happening in daily life and what kind of support is most likely to help.
          </p>
          <div class="hero-buttons">
            <a href="/book/" class="btn btn-primary">
              <svg class="icon icon-sm" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <path d="M8 7V3m8 4V3m-9 8h10M5 21h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z"/>
              </svg>
              Book a Consultation
            </a>
            <a href="/process/" class="btn btn-secondary">
              What to Expect
              <svg class="icon icon-sm" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <path d="M9 18l6-6-6-6"/>
              </svg>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="hero-visual">
          <div class="hero-image-wrapper animate-float-gentle">
            <img
              src="/res/Dr_Anita_Sharma_Personal_Photo.jpg"
              alt="Dr Anita Sharma in a professional portrait at the clinic"
              class="hero-image"
              loading="eager"
              width="400"
              height="500"
            />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CARE APPROACH SECTION -->
    <section class="main-section section-blush" aria-labelledby="approach-title">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2 id="approach-title">How Care Is Approached</h2>
        <p>Built on principles of understanding, clarity, and meaningful outcomes</p>
      </div>

      <div class="features-grid">
        <article class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg class="icon icon-lg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path d="M8 12h.01M12 12h.01M16 12h.01M21 12c0 4.418-4.03 8-9 8a9.863 9.863 0 01-4.255-.949L3 20l1.395-3.72C3.512 15.042 3 13.574 3 12c0-4.418 4.03-8 9-8s9 3.582 9 8z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Listening Before Deciding</h3>
          <p>The first goal is understanding the pattern clearly, not rushing to a one-line conclusion.</p>
        </article>

        <article class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg class="icon icon-lg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path d="M9 12h6m-6 4h6m2 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Treatment Explained Plainly</h3>
          <p>Medication, therapy, parent guidance, and developmental pathways are discussed in understandable language.</p>
        </article>

        <article class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg class="icon icon-lg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Function Matters</h3>
          <p>Better sleep, steadier mood, improved concentration, school functioning, and family life are treated as real outcomes.</p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- BACKGROUND SECTION -->
    <section class="main-section section-white" aria-labelledby="background-title">
      <div class="content-narrow">
        <h2 id="background-title">Training and Clinical Background</h2>
        <ul class="check-list">
          <li>
            <svg class="icon icon-md text-accent" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
            </svg>
            <span>MD Psychiatry, Guru Gobind Singh Medical College and Hospital, Faridkot</span>
          </li>
          <li>
            <svg class="icon icon-md text-accent" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
            </svg>
            <span>MBBS, Universal College of Medical Sciences</span>
          </li>
          <li>
            <svg class="icon icon-md text-accent" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
            </svg>
            <span>Senior Residency at AIIMS Rishikesh and IHBAS Delhi</span>
          </li>
          <li>
            <svg class="icon icon-md text-accent" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
            </svg>
            <span>Clinical work spanning adult psychiatry, child development, parent guidance, and structured outpatient care</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CLINIC ENVIRONMENT SECTION -->
    <section class="main-section section-cream" aria-labelledby="environment-title">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2 id="environment-title">Clinic Environment</h2>
        <p>The clinic experience is designed to feel calm, direct, and easier to navigate for both adults and families.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="gallery-grid">
        <figure class="gallery-item">
          <img src="/res/Location_street_view_distance.jpg" alt="Clinic exterior and nearby street approach in Greater Noida" loading="lazy"/>
          <figcaption>Exterior and arrival area</figcaption>
        </figure>
        <figure class="gallery-item">
          <img src="/res/mind-grace-entry-n-reception.jpg" alt="Front desk and waiting area at Mind Grace Clinic" loading="lazy"/>
          <figcaption>Front desk and waiting area</figcaption>
        </figure>
        <figure class="gallery-item">
          <img src="/res/mind-grace-consultation-room.jpg" alt="Consultation room at Mind Grace Clinic with a calm clinical setting" loading="lazy"/>
          <figcaption>Consultation room</figcaption>
        </figure>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- RESEARCH SECTION -->
    <section class="main-section section-white" aria-labelledby="research-title">
      <div class="content-narrow">
        <h2 id="research-title">Research and Professional Interests</h2>
        <ul class="check-list">
          <li>
            <svg class="icon icon-md text-accent" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
            </svg>
            <span>Published work on family burden in substance dependence and primary care psychiatry proceedings</span>
          </li>
          <li>
            <svg class="icon icon-md text-accent" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
            </svg>
            <span>Participation in academic and continuing medical education forums including psychiatry and addiction-related programs</span>
          </li>
          <li>
            <svg class="icon icon-md text-accent" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
            </svg>
            <span>Clinical interest in practical outpatient care for anxiety, mood concerns, ADHD, development, and parent support</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
        <div class="notice-box">
          <p>If you are mainly trying to understand whether this clinic feels like the right fit, the <a href="/process/">process page</a> and <a href="/faq/">FAQ page</a> are often the best next steps.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
</BaseLayout>
